  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC398">
        <l>kaṇṭī reṉṟā koṇṭī reṉṟā</l>
	<l>ceṉṟa teṉṟā pōyiṟ ṟeṉṟā</l>
	<l>vaṉṟi yaṉaittum viṉāvoṭu civaṇi</l>
	<l>niṉṟavaḻi yicaikkuṅ kiḷavi yeṉpa.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/211/mode/1up">211</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/212/mode/1up">212</ref>.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, ivai viṉaiyiya loḻittuniṉṟa oḻipu kaṭṭurai yeṭuttatu.</p>
<p>, iṅṅaṉam, viṉāvoṭupaṭṭu niṉṟavaḻiyāyakkāl acaiccollāyniṟkum eṉpatukaruttu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu :</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC425-Iḷam-cit1">
<l>'kaṇṭīrō, kaṇṭīrō'</l>
<l>'koṇṭīrō, koṇṭīrō'</l>
<l>'ceṉṟatē, ceṉṟatē'</l>
<l>'pōyiṟṟē, pōyiṟṟē'</l></lg>
<p>eṉa viṉāvoṭupaṭṭavaḻi aṭukki acainilaiyāy niṟkum. avviṉāvoṭu civaṇākkāl viṉaiccollēyām eṉpatu. 'aṉṟiyaṉaittum' eṉpatu, avaiyiṟṟait tokai koṭuttuk kūṟiṉavāṟu.</p>
<p>'viṉāvoṭu civaṇi' eṉpatu, ā ō eṉṉum viṉākkaḷaik kaṭaiyāttu niṉṟavaḻi eṉṟavāṟu.	(29)</p>
    </body>
  </text>

